Facilyn: The marginal reaction check asks: "Which action provides the greatest return per unit invested?" This helps you optimize your use of time, money, and energy.

Facilyn: Consider your example decision alongside other possible actions. How does it compare in terms of return on investment?

How would you evaluate your decision against this check?

